section.section:
This subsection does not apply to a visit by an inmate to a medical unit or a physician, dentist, or optometrist if the visit is:
required as a part of the intake process;
required for an initial physical examination;
due to a referral by a nurse or physician's assistant;
provided during a follow-up visit that is initiated by a medical professional from the local correctional facility;
initiated by a medical or mental health staff member of the local correctional facility; or
required for necessary treatment.
